_sText:
Fun Yard Extreme Towers :-)

This is my first map in the destruction area. 
I've always enjoyed tearing stuff apart in videogames so why not make
a few more for source?
Two skyscrapers with highly destructable top floors
and large crushing objects! When falling down, make sure to hit the water :D.
Lot's of AMMO!!!
Map should be played on strong machines because of performance issues.
It never really crashed, but you do feel the engine working hard on it :).
Not for serious gaming, just FUN!

If this map get's some positive feedback, I might make some more.

Greet's

The Dead Walk aka HOLY_BlackSkull (in the old old old days...) 

Thanks to: reibekuchen and ThrillSkull for testing the map!
